程序包 org.group4

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CombatSystem
    This class aims to create a combat system.
    GameMusic
    This class is used to deal with all the background music in the game
    JavaSoundRecorder
    This class is used to records the user voice in a new thread.
    Main
    This is the Main class to launch the game and initialise the game interface
    Player
    This class can be used to create a character object in the story, which is mainly used in the combat system.
    Speech2Text
    This class is used when building an object to connect Speech-to-Text API.
    Text2Speech
    This class connect the Text-to-Speech API and play the voice that it generates
    WatsonAssistant
    This class contains the main structure and main logic of the whole game.
